Market Segmentation: 
Pet wearable market is segmented on the basis of product, technology, animal type, application and end-use. The growth among segments helps you analyse niche pockets of growth and strategies to approach the market and determine your core application areas and the difference in your target markets.
On the basis of product, pet wearable market is segmented into smart collar, smart camera, smart harness & vest, tags, monitors, trackers and translators.
Based on technology, the pet wearable market is segmented into rfid, gps, sensors and others.
Based on animal type, the pet wearable market is segmented into companion and livestock.
Based on application, the pet wearable market is segmented into identification & tracking, behaviour monitoring & control, facilitation, safety & security and medical diagnosis & treatment.
The pet wearable market is also segmented on the basis of end-use into commercial and household.
